FORM DB_UPD_ZVSA15VEN .
*.process data base updates/inserts/deletes.........................*
LOOP AT TOTAL.
  CHECK <ACTION> NE ORIGINAL.
MOVE <VIM_TOTAL_STRUC> TO ZVSA15VEN.
  IF <ACTION> = UPDATE_GELOESCHT.
    <ACTION> = GELOESCHT.
  ENDIF.
  CASE <ACTION>.
   WHEN NEUER_GELOESCHT.
IF STATUS_ZVSA15VEN-ST_DELETE EQ GELOESCHT.
     READ TABLE EXTRACT WITH KEY <VIM_XTOTAL_KEY>.
     IF SY-SUBRC EQ 0.
